  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>You'll be spoilt for choice at the continental buffet breakfast with cereal, fresh pastries, cold meats and cheese, fruit, traditional Italian cakes and coffee.</p>
<p>For dinner, you'll have four courses with plenty of choices. The food is fresh, plentiful and homemade. You will start off with several tables filled with antipasti, a salad buffet, selection of breads, oils and balsamic vinegars and platters of mixed vegetables. First course is served to the table and is normally soup or pasta. Next up you'll be treated to fish, meat or a vegetarian, depending on what you have selected. Finally it's back up to the buffet table to feast your eyes on the daily selection of deserts including dishes such as panna cotta, tiramisu, gelato, the list goes on!</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala meals are included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
